                <div class="paragraph1">
                    <strong>PERSPECTIVE</strong>
                    <p>
                        Develop StuM School in line with the orientation, policy, and overall development strategy of StuM University (StuM), taking a pioneering role in international joint training and international cooperation,
                        internationalizing the curriculum and approaching global higher education standards.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Maximize the combined strength from all resources, especially prioritizing the exploitation of values from the unit’s unique characteristics; promote connectivity, linkage, and comprehensive cooperation
                        with units within StuM University, Hanoi, and with agencies, organizations, businesses, and localities domestically and internationally to create added value and unique products.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="paragraph2">
                    <strong>GENERAL OBJECTIVE</strong>
                    <p>
                        To train, conduct scientific research, and transfer technology oriented towards international accreditation standards based on the foundation of basic science, applied science, interdisciplinary science,
                        and knowledge transfer, contributing to increasing the internationalization index within StuM University, Hanoi, providing high-quality human resources and scientific-technological products that meet international standards for national development.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="paragraph3">
                    <strong>SPECIFIC OBJECTIVES AND KEY TASKS</strong>
                    <p>
                        For the period 2020 – 2025, the StuM University has the following objectives and key tasks:
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="paragraph4">
                    <strong>1. Perfect the organizational model and high autonomy mechanism combined with modern university management to create a breakthrough in human resource development, especially high-quality human resources and talent utilization</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Perfect the model, organizational structure, and innovate university management</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Build and operate a digital university</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Develop and implement autonomy projects</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Strengthen the training and development of faculty members and scientific departments</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Attract, recruit, and retain highly qualified staff and experts</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Implement preferential policies, value talent, while simultaneously motivating and encouraging, creating motivation</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="paragraph5">
                    <strong>2. Continue to innovate training work to improve the quality of human resources according to societal needs</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Develop high-quality training programs according to societal needs</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Diversify training models and methods, improve quality and aim for international accreditation</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Diversify forms, methods, and policies of student recruitment</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Enhance the uniqueness of training programs and learners</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Continue to innovate teaching methods towards “individualization”</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Focus on tightly integrating scientific research with training</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Promote the development of science and technology based on applied research and innovation</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Perfect the management mechanism and policies on science and technology</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Enhance activities, increase scientific and technological products</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="paragraph6">
                    <strong>3. Strengthen cooperation and development to attract resources and establish StuM University as one of the major academic and international exchange centers of StuM</strong>
