                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Increase sustainable financial resources for the development of StuM University</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Diversify financial resources</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Invest in development and modernize infrastructure to meet the requirements of training, scientific research, and high-quality services</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="paragraph7">
