                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Improving the quality of undergraduate education.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Organizing management and postgraduate training.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Attracting international students.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Developing StuM University’s student body.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Enhancing the quality and diversity of scientific and technological activities.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Expanding international cooperation and attracting international human resources.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Applying information technology in management and teaching activities.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Establishing the StuM University brand.</span></li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: SVN-Poppins; ">Implementing activities at the Hoa Lac campus.</span></li>
